
Sign Language is a visual means of communicating using gestures, facial expression, and body language. Hand gesture is one of the commonly 
used mode of communication by the people who have hearing and speaking deficiency generally called Deaf And Mute. It is the only mode of communication 
to communicate among themselves or with normal people. Hence in this paper introduced software which presents a system prototype that is able to 
automatically recognize sign language(ASL) to help deaf and mute people to communicate more effectively with each other or normal people.
